OL,3,C'The sound of the car hitting people
OL,4,Cwill live with me forever'
OL,6,FNearly 80 people have spoken of the
OL,7,Flife changing injuries and ongoing
OL,8,Fimpact of being hit by Paul Doyle's
OL,9,Fcar as it ploughed through crowds of
OL,10,FLiverpool fans in may 2025.
OL,12,F78 people submitted victim personal
OL,13,Fstatements to Liverpool Crown Court as
OL,14,Fpart of his sentencing, many
OL,15,Fdescribing "emotional and
OL,16,Fpsychological injury".
