OL,6,F"I felt an overwhelming pain in my leg
OL,7,Fand looked up to see Teddy's pushchair
OL,8,Fon its side further up the road. I
OL,9,Fthought my Teddy was dead. I thought I
OL,10,Fwas next. I thought my children would
OL,11,Fgrow up without a mother."
OL,13,FMs Aldridge said her injuries made her
OL,14,Ffeel "disgusting, disfigured and
OL,15,Fbroken," that she has been diagnosed
OL,16,Fwith a lifelong condition called Morel-
OL,17,FLavaellee Lesion and suffers from
OL,18,Fsevere back and hip pain from
OL,19,Fprolonged use of crutches.
