OL,6,FShe said: "Teddy hasn't been in a
OL,7,Fpushchair since that day. My leg will
OL,8,Fnever be the same again. I will never
OL,9,Fbe the same again. I am scarred for
OL,10,Flife."
OL,12,FMeanwhile a Merseyside Police Officer
OL,13,Fhas recalled the "sickening" noise of
OL,14,Fbodies being thrown into the air after
OL,15,Fthey were hit by the car.
OL,17,FSergeant Dan Hamilton said: "The
OL,18,Fdistress of seeing the crowd scatter
OL,19,Fin panic and bodies being thrown into
OL,20,Fthe air is something that will stay
OL,21,Fwith me forever.
