OL,6,F"The noise was sickening, dull thuds
OL,7,Fthat are difficult to describe and
OL,8,Fimpossible to forget. I remember lying
OL,9,Fon the floor thinking 'This is it; I'm
OL,10,Fgoing to die."
OL,12,FLiverpool Crown Court was told 54-year-
OL,13,Fold Doyle flew into a "rage" and
OL,14,Fploughed through the crowd of more
OL,15,Fthan 100 people in the space of two
OL,16,Fminutes.
OL,18,FOther victims told the court about
OL,19,Fpanic attacks, post traumatic stress
OL,20,Fsyndrome and suicidal thoughts.
